com.sun.identity.saml2.assertion.impl

Class SubjectConfirmationImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.saml2.assertion.impl.SubjectConfirmationImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SubjectConfirmation

    public class SubjectConfirmationImpl
extends Object
implements SubjectConfirmation
    The SubjectConfirmation provides the means for a relying party to verify the correspondence of the subject of the assertion with the party with whom the relying party is communicating.
